    "description": "Curefit invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Backend Developer at our Coimbatore location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Curefit:\nCurefit is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Learning & development budget\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Curefit!",
